    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1947-02-28T09:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1947-02-28T09:00:00-05:00" n="44"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d44">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.00/2–2847: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister-Counselor of Embassy in China</hi> (<persName
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Butterworth</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Nanking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1947-02-28T22:00:00+08:00"
                            >February 28, 1947—10 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received March 1—5:48 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>401. Following from Changchun.</p>
                <p>“71, February 26, 3 p.m. Nationalists have lost important points of Nungan,
                    Wanpaoshan, Taolaichao, Chengtsukai and Chiu-tai, presumably with commensurate
                    loss military strength. Nationalist front northwest of Changchun now weak.
                    Tehui, with about two Government regiments, is cut off by interposition strong
                    Communist forces at Puhai. On east Communists believe to have arrived in
                    vicinity Yinmaho.</p>
                <p>Nationalist reinforcements in unknown number have arrived Changchun from south in
                    past 2 days. Clubb.”</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Butterworth</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
